  "section": "2.1: Quests and combat, unlock Miscellania",
  "stepText": "Do Another Slice of H.A.M., doing the Tears of Guthix quest (don’t participate in the minigame yet) while in the Lumbridge Swamp Cave. Buy one moving-over-distance sphere from Oldak to Dorgesh-Kaan (1 noted molten glass and 2 law runes). Kill Cave Goblins for Rag and Bone Man II. Take the train to Keldagrim for the diary. Use a gold bar (or ore) on Dondakan to progress Between a Rock.…\n",
